## navbarVerticalAlign

Vertically center elements in the navbar depending on the value of its height.

### Parameters

-   `navbarHeight` **[string][1]**  (optional, default `defaultProps['$navbar-height']`)
-   `elementHeight` **[string][1]** 

Returns **[string][1]**
